column9: Emporio Armani sunglasses model 4263U 6326/73 feature a classic aviator design with a modern twist. The striped dark green acetate frame adds a unique and stylish touch perfectly complemented by solid brown lenses that provide only UV protection. Designed with attention to detail and superior craftsmanship these sunglasses offer both durability and comfort for everyday wear. The timeless aviator shape ensures a sophisticated look making them suitable for various occasions from casual outings to formal events. Lightweight and elegant they combine practicality with refined style reflecting Emporio Armanis signature blend of contemporary fashion and classic design. These sunglasses are a versatile accessory for those who value both function and luxury.
